test.sql: SELECT "Staples"."Call Center Region" AS "Call Center Region", "Staples"."Order ID" AS "Order ID", "Staples"."Product Container" AS "Product Container", AVG("Staples"."Gross Profit") AS "avg:Gross Profit:ok", CAST(EXTRACT(MONTH FROM "Staples"."Order Date") AS INTEGER) AS "mn:Order Date:ok", SUM("Staples"."Price") AS "sum:Price:ok", CAST(EXTRACT(YEAR FROM "Staples"."Order Date") AS INTEGER) AS "yr:Order Date:ok" FROM "Staples" WHERE (("Staples"."Call Center Region" = 'WEST') AND ("Staples"."Discount" >= 0.27489599999999997) AND ("Staples"."Discount" <= 0.39001000000000002) AND ((("Staples"."Order ID" >= '1') AND ("Staples"."Order ID" <= '35361')) OR (("Staples"."Order ID" >= '35363') AND ("Staples"."Order ID" <= '9991'))) AND ("Staples"."Product Container" = 'MEDIUM BOX') AND (CAST(EXTRACT(MONTH FROM "Staples"."Order Date") AS INTEGER) IN (1, 4, 7, 10))) GROUP BY 1, 2, 3, 5, 7
